<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>the addSignature function in S3.php already supports several query variables - ?acl, ?torrent, etc:</p>

<p>$sig_str .= '/'.parse_url($path, PHP_URL_PATH);
if (strpos($path, '?location') !== false) {
    $sig_str .= '?location';
}
else if (strpos($path, '?acl') !== false) {
    $sig_str .= '?acl';
}
else if (strpos($path, '?torrent') !== false) {
    $sig_str .= '?torrent';
}</p>

<p>the only thing that is missing is ?versions</p>

<p>patch:
else if (strpos($path, '?versions') !== false) {
     $sig_str .= '?versions';
}</p>

